(9, 'Finance Accounting Staff (AR / AP / Cashier) - Surabaya Based-PT Jones Lang LaSalle ', '<div class=\"unselectable wrap-text\" id=\"job_description\"> <div><strong>Requirements:</strong></div>    <ul>  	<li>Candidate must possess Bachelor Degree (Accounting, Finance, or Tax)</li>  	<li>Have a good communication skill in English is <strong>a plus point</strong></li>  	<li>At least 1 year(s) of working experience as Finance &amp; Accounting Administration</li>  	<li>Strong knowledge about invoicing, AR, AP, and GL is <strong>Mandatory</strong></li>  	<li>Preferable if have a knowledge about Accounting System (MYOB for example)</li>  	<li>Good team player, very strong in Microsoft Excel, and good communication skill</li>  	<li>Based in&nbsp;<strong>Surabaya</strong></li>  </ul> </div>', '<ul class=\"list-unstyled hidden-xs\" id=\"job_desc_detail_9\">  <li>Requirements: Candidate must possess Bachelor Degree (Accounting, Finance, or Tax). Have a good communication skill in English is a plus point. At...</li>																													</ul>', '<div class=\"panel panel-clean\"> 				<div class=\"panel-body position_panel\"> 				    					<div class=\"col-lg-2 col-md-2 col-sm-3 col-xs-12\">						 						<div class=\"logo_sm_wrap\"> 							<img id=\"company_logo\" alt=\"Finance Accounting Staff (AR/AP/Cashier) - Surabaya Based - PT Jones Lang LaSalle - Logo\" 								data-original=\"https://siva.jsstatic.com/id/2453/images/sol/2453_logo_0_7608338.jpg\"> 						</div>						 					</div> 					<div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-sm-5 col-xs-12\">					    										   <div class=\"job-position-wrap\">						         						<h1 id=\"position_title\" class=\"job-position\">Finance Accounting Staff (AR/AP/Cashier) - Surabaya Based</h1>     						<div id=\"company_name\" class=\"company_name\">     							    							        							        <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.jobstreet.co.id/en/companies/714527-pt-jones-lang-lasalle\">PT Jones Lang LaSalle</a>     							      				