(10, 'HEAD OF MARKETING USED CAR DEPARTMENT-PT Indomobil Finance Indonesia ', '<div class=\"unselectable wrap-text\" id=\"job_description\"> <div style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>ROLES &amp; RESPONSIBILITIES:</strong></div>    <ul>  	<li style=\"text-align:justify\">Identify Member &amp; Channel Marketing capabilities needed; develop team goals, structure, annual/quarterly plans, roadmaps and budgets</li>  	<li style=\"text-align:justify\">Branch marketing and merchandising strategies, driving member/prospect engagement in the retail channel, and growing brand equity</li>  	<li style=\"text-align:justify\">Manage the full lifecycle of the team&rsquo;s strategic initiatives, including situation analyses, proposed strategies and tactics, budgets, timelines, execution and reporting/evaluation</li>  </ul>    <div style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</div>    <div style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>REQUIREMENTS:</strong></div>    <div style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</div>    <ul>  	<li style=\"text-align:justify\">Minimum 5 years experience as Manager in Used Car vehicle financing services from Multifinance Company</li>  	<li style=\"text-align:justify\">Having experience in managing strategically marketing programs, ideally in a financial services or member-focused organization</li>  	<li style=\"text-align:justify\">Deep range of strategic and executional skills (planning, strategy, execution, budget management, relationship management)</li>  	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Profound&nbsp; knowledge of marketing strategies of Used Car vehicle financing services, loyalty programs and regulations valuable</strong></li>  	<li style=\"text-align:justify\">Proven ability to develop, execute, measure and optimize marketing programs that drive business results; a portfolio showcasing successful multi-channel campaigns highly valuable</li>  	<li style=\"text-align:justify\">Highly organized self-starter with expertise managing multiple projects simultaneously