style=\"text-align: justify;\">  	&nbsp;</div>  <div style=\"text-align: justify;\">  	<strong>Our value is :</strong></div>  <div style=\"text-align: justify;\">  	&nbsp;</div>  <div style=\"text-align: justify;\">  	<strong>Customer Focus; </strong>We highly care about our customer, our team always make sure that our customer get an extraordinary shopping experiences and we always provide only a excellent product &amp; excellent service</div>  <div style=\"text-align: justify;\">  	&nbsp;</div>  <div style=\"text-align: justify;\">  	<strong>Originally</strong><strong>; </strong>Our team always looking for a new ways to serve our customer better than before, we never stop learning and we loves to grow</div>  <div style=\"text-align: justify;\">  	&nbsp;</div>  <div style=\"text-align: justify;\">  	<strong>Partnership; </strong>We sure about one thing: team work will bring us to perfection &amp; success together, so we do care about each other and build a good communication within our team</div>  <div style=\"text-align: justify;\">  	&nbsp;</div>  <div style=\"text-align: justify;\">  	<strong>Responsibility;</strong> Our team realized, our customer&#39;s satisfaction depend to our product &amp; services, that makes us being responsible to every aspect of our services and every task we are doing</div>  <div style=\"text-align: justify;\">  	&nbsp;</div>  <div style=\"text-align: justify;\">  	<strong>Passion; </strong>We believe our passion will drive us to be excellent in what we do, that&#39;s the reason why our team always in high spirit &amp; full of passion in serving our customer</div>  </p> 							</div>', '<p id=\"why_join_us\" class=\"cmpy_desc_p\"><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">  	Being part of LOTTE GROUP and one of top 500 Company in the world, both Lotte Shopping Indonesia &amp; Lotte Mart Indonesia have shared knowledge &amp; competencies from our culture diversed network. Currently we have 45 Stores across indonesia and more than 290 Stores in 4 Countries in total and yet, we still continued grow &amp; expanding.</div>  <div style=\"text-align: justify;\">  	&nbsp;</div>  <div style=\"text-align: justify;\">  	With well experienced &amp; strong Management Team, Lotte Shopping Indonesia &amp; Lotte Mart Indonesia has growing fast through years. Our Management Principle is :</div>  <ul>  	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">  		<strong>Strengthening Core Competencies</strong></li>  	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">  		<strong>On Site Management</strong></li>  	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">  		<strong>Developing Talent</strong></li>  	<li style=\"text-align: justify;\">  		<strong>Enhancing Brand Value</strong></li>  </ul>  <div style=\"text-align: justify;\">  	&nbsp;</div>  <div style=\"text-align: justify;\">  	We take care our team the same way we take care about our customer, we realized that happy and developed talent will drive our success to achive our Vision to be Asia&#39;s Top 10 Company in 2018.</div>  <div style=\"text-align: justify;\">  	&nbsp;</div>  <div style=\"text-align: justify;\">  	Due to our rapid expansion, we invite you to join us ..... <strong>NURTURE YOUR CAREER WITH US!</strong></div>  </p>', '<img class=\"img-company-logo\" id=\"img_company_logo_5\" src=\"https://siva.jsstatic.com/id/808/images/logo/808_logo_0_230525.jpg\" alt=\"Lowongan PT Lotte Shopping Indonesia\">', 'Pemasaran/Pengembangan Bisnis', ' &#62; Teknisi/Programer Perangkat Lunak', 'Automobil / Mesin Tambahan Automotif / Kendaraan ', 'Jakarta Raya ', 'jabodetabek', 'PT Lotte Shopping Indonesia ', 'Jl. Lingkar Luar Selatan Kav.5 & 6 Ciracas Jakarta', 'https://www.jobstreet.co.id/id/job/assistant-manager-it-programmer-3035026?fr=J&searchRequestToken=86caa7a9-65e9-47ae-b060-f86f18565fcc&sectionRank=5', 'Assistant-Manager-IT-Programmer', 'Ditayangkan: 26-August-2019 ', ' 							  							  Tutup pada 25-September-2019', '2019-08-26', '2019-09-25', 'open'),
(32, 'Accounting Closing Staff-PT LG ELectronics Indonesia ', '<div class=\"unselectable wrap-text\" id=\"job_description\"> <div><strong>Requirement:</strong></div><ul><li>Bachelor&rsquo;s degree majoring Accounting</li><li>Prefer 2-3 years equivalent experience</li><li>Computer literate (Ms. office, internet, ERP applications)</li><li>Fluent in English both oral and written.</li><li>Having good analytical skill, logic thinking, honest, high integrity and self-motivated person.</li><li>Have strong interpersonal skill, like to work in a dynamic environment, perform excellent work both individual &amp; in a team,&nbsp;working under pressure, working endurance, responsible person &amp; able perform with minimum supervision</li></ul><div>&nbsp;</div><div><strong>Job Describtion :</strong></div><ul><li>Expense voucher checking</li><li>Input GL Adjustment</li><li>Input GNMS Voucher</li><li>Fixed Asset controller</li><li>BS &amp; PL Analysis</li><li>GFVS Monitoring</li></ul><div>&nbsp;</div> </div>', '<ul class=\"list-unstyled hidden-xs\" id=\"job_desc_detail_6\">  <li>Requirement: Bachelor&rsquo;s degree majoring Accounting. Prefer 2-3 years equivalent experience. Computer literate (Ms. office, internet, ERP...</li>																													</ul>', '<div class=\"panel panel-clean\"> 				<div class=\"panel-body position_panel\"> 				    					<div class=\"col-lg-2 col-md-2 col-sm-3 col-xs-12\">						 						<div class=\"logo_sm_wrap\"> 							<img id=\"company_logo\" alt=\"Accounting Closing Staff - PT LG ELectronics Indonesia - Logo\" 								data-original=\"https://siva.jsstatic.com/id/64/images/sol/64_logo_0_879560.png\"> 						</div>						 					</div> 					<div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-sm-5 col-xs-12\">					    										   <div class=\"job-position-wrap\">						         						<h1 id=\"position_title\" class=\"job-position\">Accounting Closing Staff</h1>     						<div id=\"company_name\" class=\"company_name\">     							    							        							        <a ta