																		</div> 												   </div> 					</div> 					<div class=\"col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-sm-4 col-xs-12 table-location-div\"> 					    <div class=\"job-info-wrap\">     						                            <div id=\"salary\" class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-sx-12\"></div>     						<div id=\"experience\" class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-sx-12\">     							<p id=\"years_of_experience\" class=\"main_desc_detail\"> 	<span class=\"main_desc_icon\"> 		<span class=\"icon-briefcase icon_left experience\"></span> 	</span> 	<span id=\"years_of_experience\"> 			Min 2 tahun (Pegawai (non-manajemen & non-supervisor))  		</span> </p> 				 </div>                                 						<div id=\"location\" class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-sx-12\">     							<p class=\"main_desc_detail\" > 	<span id=\"work_location\" class=\"main_desc_icon\"> 		<span class=\"icon-location icon_left location\"></span> 	</span> 			<span id=\"single_work_location\" class=\"single_work_location\"> 			Indonesia - Jawa Timur - Gresik		</span> 	</p> 			 			 			</div>     					</div> 					</div> 				</div> 			</div>', '<div id=\"company_overview_all\" class=\"company-overview wrap-text\"> 								<p id=\"company_overview\" class=\"cmpy_desc_p\"><div> <div style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>PT Hanampi Sejahtera Kahuripan (PT HSK)</strong> is the first and largest controlled-release fertilizer producer in Indonesia and Southeast Asia.&nbsp;&nbsp; PT HSK fertilizer production plants and R&amp;D centre are located in Gresik, East Jawa province.&nbsp; PT HSK fertilizer products are mainly use in oil palm, paddy rice, corn, tobacco, sugarcane and other tropical crops.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</div>  <div style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</div>  <div style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>PT Hanampi Sejahtera Kahuripan (PT HSK)</strong> was incorporated in Indonesia in year 2009 and is jointly owned by 2 Indonesian companies and 1 foreign company.&nbsp; The company via three parties&rsquo; cooperation complements each other&rsquo;s strength, promote the use of slow release fertilizer and compound fertilizer in Indonesia and South East Asia, and contribute to fertilizer upgrade and agricultural development in this region.</div>  <div style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</div> </div>  <div style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</div>  <div style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Product &amp; Services</strong></div>  <div> <div> <div style=\"text-align:justify\">NPK Compound Fertilizer</div>  <div style=\"text-align:justify\">Sulfur Coated Urea (SCU)</div>  <div style=\"text-align:justify\">Controlled Release Fertilizer</div>  <div style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</div> </div> </div>  <div style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</div></p> 							</div>', '<p id=\"why_join_us\" class=\"cmpy_desc_p\"><div> <div style=\"text-align:justify\">PT Hanampi Sejahtera Kahuripan (PT HSK) was incorporated in Indonesia in year 2009 and is jointly owned by 2 Indonesian companies and 1 foreign company.&nbsp; The completed first phase project including Sulfur coated Urea fertilizer plant with capacity of 50,000mt/year, Compound fertilizer plant with capacity of 100,000mt/year and Bulk Blend fertilizer plant with capacity of 300,000mt/year.&nbsp; The company via three parties&rsquo; cooperation complements each other&rsquo;s strength, promote the use of slow release fertilizer and compound fertilizer in Indonesia and South East Asia, and contribute to fertilizer upgrade and agricultural development in this region.</div>  <div style=\"text-align:justify\">PT. Hanampi Sejahtera Kahuripan is jointly owned by below 3 companies:-</div>  <div style=\"text-align:justify\">&sup2;&nbsp; PT. Indo Pupuk Sejahtera (a subsidiary of Group Sejahtera) is a company that distributes fertilizer, pesticide, irrigation, tractor and other agricultural products in Indonesia and Malaysia. It has strong marketing team and extensive distribution network.<br /> <br /> &sup2;&nbsp; Hanfeng Slow-Release Fertilizer Investment Co., Limited is a wholly owned subsidiary of Hanfeng Evergreen Inc. (a listed company in Canada). Hanfeng has the advance technologies for slow release fertilizer and compound fertilizer. Currently, it has a few fertilizer factories in China with total production capacities of 725,000mt/year.<br /> <br /> &sup2;&nbsp; PT. Kurnia Sentosa Kahuripan (a subsidiary of Makin Group) is an oil palm plantation company and currently is growing more than 100,000ha of oil palm crop in Indonesia.<br /> <br /> Strategically located in Gresik near Surabaya, PT HSK has production plants producing coated urea, coated NPK compound, coated NPK blend and compound fertilizer.</div>  <div style=\"text-align:justify\">The controlled release fertilizers can improve fertilizer effectiveness and efficiency, while reducing environment damage as compared to conventional fertilizers.&nbsp;&nbsp; Indonesia local fertilizers producers are consist of government controlled producers and a handful of private producers.&nbsp; There is no local production of controlled release fertilizer and has limited high quality NPK compound fertilizers.&nbsp; The imported slow release fertilizers are too expensive to penetrate significantly into Indonesia market.</div>  <div style=\"text-align:justify\">The demand for slow release fertilizers in Indonesia is growing due to the modernization of the agricultural industry and growing environmental concerns.&nbsp; PT HSK is addressing this demand by producing these products locally to save cost for end-users.&nbsp; PT HSK has positioned itself to lead the controlled release fertilizer industry in Indonesia.</div> </div></p>', '<img class=\"img-company-logo\" id=\"img_company_logo_3\" src=\"https://siva.jsstatic.com/id/32394/images/logo/32394_logo_0_6902069.jpg\" alt=\"Lowongan PT Hanampi Sejahtera Kahuripan\">', 'Pembelian/Manajemen Material', ' &#62; Kontrol Inventoris', 'Properti / Real Estate ', 'Gresik (Jawa Timur) ', 'jabodetabek', 'PT Hanampi Sejahtera Kahuripan ', 'PT HANAMPI SEJAHTERA KAHURIPAN Beta Maspion Blok I, Kawasan Industri Maspion Jl Raya Manyar KM 25 Desa Manyar Sidomukti Gresik 61151 Up. Departemen HR&GA', 'https://www.jobstreet.co.id/id/job/pelaksana-elektrik-3035085?fr=J&searchRequestToken=ef061c46-4c3a-4f48-8c88-b54312241a62&sectionRank=3', 'Pelaksana-Elektrik', 'Ditayangkan: 26-August-2019 ', ' 							  							  Tutup pada 25-September-2019', '2019-08-26', '2019-09-25', 'open'),
