rience\" class=\"main_desc_detail\"> 	<span class=\"main_desc_icon\"> 		<span class=\"icon-briefcase icon_left experience\"></span> 	</span> 	<span id=\"years_of_experience\"> 			Min 1 tahun (Pegawai (non-manajemen & non-supervisor))  		</span> </p> 				 </div>                                 						<div id=\"location\" class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-sx-12\">     							<p class=\"main_desc_detail\" > 	<span id=\"work_location\" class=\"main_desc_icon\"> 		<span class=\"icon-location icon_left location\"></span> 	</span> 			<span id=\"single_work_location\" class=\"single_work_location\"> 			Indonesia - Jakarta Raya - Pantai Indah Kapuk		</span> 	</p> 			 			 			</div>     					</div> 					</div> 				</div> 			</div>', '<div id=\"company_overview_all\" class=\"company-overview wrap-text\"> 								<p id=\"company_overview\" class=\"cmpy_desc_p\"><div> <div> <div style=\"text-align:justify\">Pancake, comes in different names, tastes, toppings and variations. But this delicacy shares one thing in common: Loved and savored by everybody from every part of the world.</div>  <div style=\"text-align:justify\"><br /> Pancious is a casual dining restaurant who is dedicated to bring you the best and value-for-money pancake experience. Because whoever you are, whether you&rsquo;re young or grown-up, a food adventurer or a settler for familiar taste, you must&rsquo;ve had at least one pancake experience in your life. And our job is to capture that experience and offer it to you only in a better scale.</div>  <div style=\"text-align:justify\"><br /> As a pioneer in Jakarta&rsquo;s pancake industry, Pancious single-handedly changed the society&rsquo;s paradigm of pancake being a breakfast material. Nowadays, pancakes are enjoyed as the main course throughout the day, at anytime you please. And so far we have done a fantastic job.</div>  <div style=\"text-align:justify\"><br /> Of course taste alone won&rsquo;t suffice in this industry. It needs to be supported with great services, which luckily for us, our front-men and women are 100% dedicated to serve you and to ensure that your pancake experience is close to perfection.</div>  <div style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</div>  <div style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</div> </div> </div></p> 							</div>', '<p id=\"why_join_us\" class=\"cmpy_desc_p\"><div style=\"text-align:justify\">Being the pioneer and simply being the best is not enough to set us apart from the rest. We are already halfway through achieving our biggest dream: To become the foremost western casual dining restaurant in Indonesia. And in order to fully reach it, each day means a new day to reinvent ourselves. Each day is a challenge to outdo our yester-selves. And each day is a chance to assess what we&rsquo;ve accomplished this far and make it even better.</div></p>', '<img class=\"img-company-logo\" id=\"img_company_logo_8\" src=\"https://siva.jsstatic.com/id/15602/images/logo/15602_logo_0_6438185.jpg\" alt=\"Lowongan PT Pancious Tirta Jaya\">', 'Pembelian/Manajemen Material', ' &#62; Kontrol Inventoris', 'Properti / Real Estate ', 'Jakarta Raya - Pantai Indah Kapuk ', 'jabodetabek', 'PT Pancious Tirta Jaya ', 'Jalan Ruko Toho, Kamal Muara, North Jakarta City, Special Capital Region of Jakarta, Indonesia', 'https://www.jobstreet.co.id/id/job/staff-gudang-3035079?fr=J&searchRequestToken=ef061c46-4c3a-4f48-8c88-b54312241a62&sectionRank=8', 'Staff-Gudang', 'Ditayangkan: 26-August-2019 ', ' 							  							  Tutup pada 25-September-2019', '2019-08-26', '2019-09-25', 'open'),
(61, 'Expert Teacher for Quipper Video-PT. Quipper Edukasi Indonesia ', '<div class=\"unselectable wrap-text\" id=\"job_description\"> <div><strong>DESKRIPSI PEKERJAAN</strong></div>    <div>Secara umum, bertanggung jawab dalam pembuatan modul, soal-soal, dan penyampaian materi pembelajaran di hadapan kamera. Kami membuka kesempatan untuk para guru dan pengajar untuk bergabung bersama kami sebagai pengajar Quipper Video untuk mata pelajaran <strong>Fisika, Geografi.</strong></div>    <div>&nbsp;</div>    <div><strong>Tugas dan Tanggung Jawab</strong></div>    <ul>  	<li>Mempersiapkan modul dan materi pembelajaran sesuai mata pelajaran yang ditugaskan (Grade 7-12).&nbsp;</li>  	<li>Menyusun soal-soal dan pembahasan sesuai dengan materi pembelajaran.</li>  	<li>Mempresentasikan materi pembelajaran di hadapan kamera.</li>  	<li>Tugas lain yang berkaitan dengan Divisi Konten.</li>  </ul>    <div>&nbsp;</div>    <div><strong>Persyaratan dan Kualifikasi</strong></div>    <ul>  	<li>Berijazah minimal Sarjana (S1) jurusan Pendidikan atau jurusan lain yang setara dan berhubungan dengan pendidikan.</li>  	<li>Memiliki pengalaman minimal 1 tahun&nbsp;sebagai Guru/Pengajar.&nbsp;Memiliki pengalaman mengajar di bimbingan belajar akan menjadi nilai tambah.</li>  	<li>Menguasai teknik mengajar, pembuatan modul pembelajaran dan kemampuan presentasi yang baik.</li>  	<li>Memiliki kreatifitas dalam pengembangan bahan ajar</li>  	<li>Memiliki kemampuan berkomunikasi yang baik dan efisien.</li>  	<li>Percaya diri saat berhadapan dengan kamera.</li>  	<li>Bersedia untuk bekerja di daerah Jakarta Selatan.</li>  </ul>    <div>&nbsp;</div>    <div><strong>Proses Perekrutan</strong></div>    <ul>  	<li>Pelamar hanya dapat melamar melalui situs ini dengan melampirkan CV dan surat lamaran terbaru.</li>  	<li>Pelamar harus mencantumkan Mata Pelajaran yang dikuasai dengan format berikut: <strong>Nama Posisi_Mata Pelajaran</strong>, contoh: <strong>Expert Teacher_Fisika</strong>.</li>  </ul>    