(108, 'IT Auditor Assurance-PT Ernst &amp; Young Indonesia ', '<div class=\"unselectable wrap-text\" id=\"job_description\"> <div>EY is one of the leading global organizations with more than 250,000 employees all over the world. There is no better time than now to join us <strong>Building a Better Working World</strong></div>    <div>&nbsp;</div>    <div>  <div><strong>Job Purpose</strong></div>    <div>As a member of the Assurance team, you&#39;ll make a technical contribution to audit engagements and internal projects. You&#39;ll actively establish internal and external relationships, and identify and escalate potential business opportunities for Ernst &amp; Young on existing engagements. With a clear focus on anticipating and identifying risks, you&#39;ll escalate issues as appropriate. You&#39;ll confirm that the work delivered to clients is of high quality and is reviewed by the next-level reviewer.</div>    <div>&nbsp;</div>    <div><strong>Your client responsibilities</strong></div>    <div>  <ul>  	<li>  	<div>Participate in assurance engagements and executing the work plan</div>  	</li>  	<li>  	<div>Work effectively as a team member, sharing responsibility, providing support, maintaining communication and updating senior team members on progress</div>  	</li>  	<li>  	<div>Help prepare for meetings with target management teams, and participate in these meetings</div>  	</li>  	<li>  	<div>Assist in preparing reports and schedules that will be delivered to clients and other parties</div>  	</li>  	<li>  	<div>Develop and maintain productive working relationships with client personnel</div>  	</li>  	<li>  	<div>Build strong internal relationships within Ernst &amp; Young Assurance and across other services</div>  	</li>  </ul>  </div>    <div><strong>Your people responsibilities</strong></div>    <ul>  	<li>  	<div>Contribute to people initiatives, including recruiting and retaining assurance professionals</div>  	</li>  	<li>  	<div>Maintain an educational program to continually develop personal skills of staff</div>  	</li>  	<li>  	<div>Understand and follow workplace policies and procedures</div>  	</li>  </ul>    <div><strong>Requirements:</strong></div>  </div>    <ul>  	<li>Candidate must possess at least Bachelor&#39;s Degree in Accounting/Audit System Information,&nbsp;Computer Science/Information Technology or equivalent.</li>  	<li>At least 1&nbsp;Year(s) of working experience in the related field is required for this position.</li>  	<li>Required Skill(s): IT audit</li>  	<li>Preferably Staff (non-management &amp; non-supervisor) specialized in Finance - Audit/Taxation or equivalent.</li>  	<li>FRESH GRADUATES WITH ACCOUNTING BACKGROUND ARE WELCOME TO APPLY</li>  </ul>    <div>Only shortlisted applicants will be notified.</div> </div>', '<ul class=\"list-unstyled hidden-xs\" id=\"job_desc_detail_2\">  <li>EY is one of the leading global organizations with more than 250,000 employees all over the world. There is no better time than now to join us...</li>																													</ul>', '<div class=\"panel panel-clean\"> 				<div class=\"panel-body position_panel\"> 				    					<div class=\"col-lg-2 col-md-2 col-sm-3 col-xs-12\">						 						<div class=\"logo_sm_wrap\"> 							<img id=\"company_logo\" alt=\"IT Auditor Assurance - PT Ernst & Young Indonesia - Logo\" 								data-original=\"https://siva.jsstatic.com/id/6397/images/sol/6397_logo_0_6060017.jpg\"> 						</div>						 					</div> 					<div class=\"col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-sm-5 col-xs-12\">					    										   <div class=\"job-position-wrap\">						         						<h1 id=\"position_title\" class=\"job-position\">IT Auditor Assurance</h1>     						<div id=\"company_name\" class=\"company_name\">     							    							        							        <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.jobstreet.co.id/en/companies/717198-pt-ernst-n-young-indonesia\">PT Ernst & Young Indonesia</a>     							      																					</div> 												   </div> 					</div> 					<div class=\"col-lg-4 col-md-4 col-sm-4 col-xs-12 table-location-div\"> 					    <div class=\"job-info-wrap\">     						                            <div id=\"salary\" class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-sx-12\"></div>     						<div id=\"experience\" class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-sx-12\">     							<p id=\"years_of_experience\" class=\"main_desc_detail\"> 	<span class=\"main_desc_icon\"> 		<span class=\"icon-briefcase icon_left experience\"></span> 	</span> 	<span id=\"years_of_experience\"> 			Min 1 tahun (Pegawai (non-manajemen & non-supervisor))  		</span> </p> 				 </div>                                 						<div id=\"location\" class=\"col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12 col-sx-12\">     							<p class=\"main_desc_detail\" > 	<span id=\"work_location\" class=\"main_desc_icon\"> 		<span class=\"icon-location icon_left location\"></span> 	</span> 			<span id=\"single_work_location\" class=\"single_work_location\"> 			Indonesia - Jakarta Raya		</span> 	</p> 			 			 			</div>     					</div> 					</div> 				</div> 			</div>', '<div id=\"company_overview_all\" class=\"company-overview wrap-text\"> 								<p id=\"company_overview\" class=\"cmpy_desc_p\"><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">EY is a global leader in Assurance, Tax, Transaction Advisory Services and Advisory.&nbsp; The insights and quality services we deliver help build trust and confidence in the capital markets and in economies the world over. We develop outstanding leaders who team to deliver on our promises to all of our stakeholders. In so doing, we play a critical role in building a better working world for our people, for our clients and for our communities.</div></p> 							</div>', '<p id=\"why_join_us\" class=\"cmpy_desc_p\"><div> <div style=\"text-align: justify;\">There is no better time than now to join us Building a Better Working World.</div>  <div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br /> EY differentiation is in teaming. We are a global leader in Assurance, Tax, Transaction Advisory Services and Advisory. Worldwide, our 250,000 people are united by our shared values and an unwavering commitment in Building a Better Working World.</div>  <div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>  <div style=\"text-align: justify;\">With our clear vision for the years ahead and commitment to developing outstanding leaders, EY is the place to begin your career. What could you achieve in a global organization that encourages you to express your ideas and share your opinions? Whenever you join us - you&rsquo;ll be surrounded by people who trust and respect you; people who&rsquo;ll open the door to experiences that will last a lifetime.</div>  <div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>  <div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>  <div style=\"text-align: justify;\">We&rsquo;ve set out a clear vision of where we expect to be in the year 2020 and have a detailed road map for reaching our objectives. As a result, you will have greater opportunity than ever before to gain insights and experiences that will last you a lifetime.</div> </div>  <div>&nbsp;</div></p>', '<img class=\"img-company-logo\" id=\"img_company_logo_2\" src=\"https://siva.jsstatic.com/id/6397/images/logo/6397_logo_0_6060017.jpg\" alt=\"Lowongan PT Ernst &amp; Young Indonesia\">', 'Logistik/Jaringan distribusi', ' &#62; Auditing', 'Transportasi / Logistik ', 'Jakarta Raya ', 'jabodetabek', 'PT Ernst &amp; Young Indonesia ', 'Jl. Jenderal Sudirman, Kota Jakarta Pusat, DKI Jakarta, Indonesia', 'https://www.jobstreet.co.id/id/job/it-auditor-assurance-3042302?fr=J&searchRequestToken=588e000b-0434-4368-eda7-5cfb8c3a85e4&sectionRank=2', 'IT-Auditor-Assurance', 'Ditayangkan: 31-August-2019 ', ' 							  							  Tutup pada 30-September-2019', '2019-08-31', '2019-09-30', 'open'),
(109, 'Trainer Head (HR &amp; GA Departement)-PT Putra Gemilang Prima ', '<div class=\"unselectable wrap-text\" id=\"job_description\"> <div style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</div>    <ul>  	<li style=\"text-align:justify\">Merencanakan seluruh kegiatan Pengembangan Skill Karyawan terutama Standart Pelayanan Departemen Store dan Kemampuan Teknis Karyawan.</li>  	<li style=\"text-align:justify\">Bertanggung jawab atas pelaksanaan kegiatan Training Pengembangan Skill Karyawan.</li>  	<li style=\"text-align:justify\">Membuat Laporan Progress Report pelaksanaan Training Pengembangan Skill Karyawan.</li>  	<li style=\"text-align:justify\">Evaluasi hasil masing-masing kegiatan yang telah dilaksanakan.</li>  </ul>    <div style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</div>    <div style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Kualifikasi :</strong></div>    <div style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</div>    <ul>  	<li style=\"text-align:justify\">Pendidikan Minimal S1 (diutamakan jurusan Psikologi/Manajemen SDM).</li>  	<li style=\"text-align:justify\">Usia&nbsp;28 - 38 tahun.</li>  	<li style=\"text-align:justify\">Pengalaman Kerja 2 - 4 tahun.</li>  	<li style=\"text-align:justify\">Pengalaman di bidang Retail.</li>  	<li style=\"text-align:justify\">Mengerti Standar Pelayanan di bidang Retail.</li>  	<li style=\"text-align:justify\">Mengerti mekanisme sistem Retail.</li>  	<li style=\"text-align:justify\">Menguasai program untuk Presentasi (Power Point).</li>  	<li style=\"text-align:justify\">Mampu berkomunikasi secara interaktif pada saat memberikan training.</li>  </ul> </div>', '<ul class=\"list-unstyled hidden-xs\" id=\"job_desc_detail_1\">  <li> Merencanakan seluruh kegiatan Pengembangan Skill Karyawan terutama Standart Pelayanan Departemen Store dan Kemampuan Teknis Karyawan. Bertanggung...</li>																													</ul>', '<div class=\"panel panel-clean\"> 				<div class=\"panel-body position_panel\"> 				    					<div class=\"col-lg-2 col-md-2 col-sm-3 col-xs-12\">						